# Skills go here.
#
# Each subdirectory becomes a skill: `<skill-name>/SKILL.md` plus any
# supporting scripts/references. Every channel inherits all skills in this
# directory by default; channels can exclude specific skills via their
# manifest's `skills.disallowed` list.
#
# See Claude Code's skill conventions:
#   https://docs.claude.com/claude-code/skills
